name: SEEDx
description: What is the project about? Built on the Binance Smart Chain, SEEDx is an AMM that uses a limit and Market order book to provide instantaneous trades, pooled liquidity, and innovative yield-generating features. Trade & Swap Quickly exchanging tokens inside 0x liquidity Fusion pools is made possible using SEEDx's swap function, while more complex trading options, like as limit orders and Market Order, are made available via the DEX Interface. They enhance the user's shopping experience. What makes your project unique? SEEDx offers 0x liquidity protocol i.e listing of new projects doesnt require liquidity. SEEDx also provides Decentralized orderbook exchange and unique Airdrop Distribution platform. History of your project.
